{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC07_LEO_070.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x13,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Can I ask you a question?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Sure, what is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "You're a clothier, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, that's right. Do I look like a nun or a soldier to you?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "No, you don't. But clothiers make clothes using cloth, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Sounds about right."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x35,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "...So why do you make things like armor using metal?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I trained to do that at the last place I worked."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "What!? Really? But making armor is a blacksmith's job..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Normally, yes. But that shop's motto was \"Clothiers who only make clothes are third-rate!\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Huh...? I don't really understand..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Well, let's see... What would you think if you saw an adventurer going around wearing a fancy dress?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "An adventurer wearing a dress? Um... I don't think it would be suitable..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Yup, that's right. Adventurers should wear armor."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "That was just one example, but each person has an outfit that's most suitable for them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "You can only call yourself a top rate clothier if you make armor and accessories. That's how they operate."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I see... So that's why you trained to make armor too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "That's right. It was pretty tough back then. I trained every day at a stall much like this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "But... While I have complaints about it, it might have been the most fun I've had in my life, too."
        }
    ]
}